[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/focus_punch">Focus Punch</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/focus_punch">Focus Punch</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user focuses its mind before launching this attack. It will fail if the user is hit before it is used.</p>